    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-07-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="271"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d271">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <gloss target="#t_CFM1">C.F.M.</gloss> Files: Lot M–88: Box 2061: <gloss
                        target="#t_CFM1">CFM</gloss> Documents</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Draft Resolution by the <gloss type="from">French
                            Delegation</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Council of Foreign
                            Ministers</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="29" xml:id="d271fn29">This resolution was discussed by the Council of
                        Foreign Ministers at its 41st Meeting, July 12, 1946, and was amended and
                        approved by the Council at its 42nd Meeting, July 12. For the agreed
                        amendment, see the Record of Decisions of the 42nd Meeting, <ref
                            target="#pg_937">p. 937</ref>; see also the United States Delegation
                        Records of the 41st and 42nd Meetings, <ref target="#pg_907">pp. 907</ref>
                        and <ref target="#pg_918">918</ref>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M.(46)</gloss> 226</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-07-11">11 July,
                            1946</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Germany</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council of Foreign Ministers hereby decides to instruct the Allied Control
                    Council <hi rend="italic">to appoint a Committee of qualified experts</hi>
                    <pb facs="0926" n="902" xml:id="pg_902"/> which shall report to the four
                    Governments by 10th August, 1946 at the latest on the following points: <list>
                        <label>1.</label>
                        <item>Steps to be taken to increase the German output of coal;</item>
                        <label>2.</label>
                        <item>General principles which should govern the apportionment of the German
                            output as between domestic consumption and exports.</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p>The Committee’s report will be discussed by the Council of Foreign Ministers
                    before 1st September, 1946.</p>
            </div>
